This is an ideaverse-OS vault.

At session start, read these files in order:
1. 00-agentic-OS/soul.md (behavioral constraints)
2. 00-agentic-OS/me.md (identity)
3. 00-agentic-OS/user.md (workflow)
4. 00-agentic-OS/compass.md (current priorities)
5. 00-agentic-OS/memory.md (decision log)
6. 00-agentic-OS/runbook.md (skill routing)

These files have auto_inject: true frontmatter.

Skills live in 60-skills/_shared/. Each is a folder with SKILL.md.

Position-addressed folders use numbered prefixes (00, 10, 20, ..., 99) with 10s spacing.

